{"tid":2118508,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有獨立媒體可以出書","createTime":"2020-07-21T13:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T08:43:54.000Z","uid":216754,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b66481ee8c62d17c43c7b67c7ad9e499714cd49","tid":2118508,"uid":216754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"話說獨立媒體 誌 唔止報導、拍紀錄片，而家仲要出本書叫《香港大道》，搵左廿個人做人物專訪（爆眼少年、老師、勇武、和理非etc），有插畫又有抗爭相、時間線整合、成個運動既用詞表，仲有記者當日既採訪觀察分析 <br />\n搞咁多嘢都真係幾癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=269090637722828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D269090637722828&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj6xOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=3eb83eb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=269090637722828</a><br />\n<br />\n可能大家覺得時間線同用詞呢啲我全部都知啦做咩要買本書黎睇，但係紙本都係一樣好重要既媒體。就算他朝一日電腦大爆炸！揸住本書，都可以將歷史傳承比下一代，下下一代，子子孫孫都要知！全部都要記撚住！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YifeOwk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYifeOwk.png&h=b806e5e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3An1twm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3An1twm.png&h=978680d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1mEZC2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1mEZC2.png&h=f89e2d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n30頁試閱<br />\n<a href=\"https://issuu.com/hkfeature/docs/hk_feature-hk_road_preview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fissuu.com%2Fhkfeature%2Fdocs%2Fhk_feature-hk_road_preview&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj6xOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=95b8ed45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://issuu.com/hkfeature/docs/hk_feature-hk_road_preview</a><br />\n<br />\n早鳥送 我不閱讀 記者札記<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLxAxYq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLxAxYq.png&h=f47006ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=889057301584424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D889057301584424&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj6xOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=61fddc95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=889057301584424</a><br />\n<br />\n最後 希望大家多多支持香港獨立媒體<br />\n同埋睇多啲書！腹有詩書氣自華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c07126ae547d484c75be3e6378ac7451479d64b","tid":2118508,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"香港獨立媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f7c8455e48bd238cf51a29db352d43955790b4","tid":2118508,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1c22762d74a08780e2d9fa4ffb77ba0ac83d60","tid":2118508,"uid":270576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef85e43e27b1fef0fdd249e040fd7bb6d0516d62","tid":2118508,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"獨媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a45994bbf95f19052140b0d8819095b93d1bd9","tid":2118508,"uid":239384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:47:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f89d9194abdd7bb9cb141919c0320344ece6ffb","tid":2118508,"uid":94219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad1d12796a521a